          Why Settle for Half-Baked Websites?
        </h2>
        
        <div class="relative">
          <p class="text-lg md:text-lg text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8 pl-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
